              <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">As a co-founder of the South Asian Liver Institute (SALi), Prof. Dr. Cherian is dedicated to providing affordable, high-quality liver care to patients across the region. His vision is to establish SALi as a center of excellence for liver treatment, research, and education.</p>
